<h1 id="greetings">Greetings!</h1>

<p>My name is <strong>W. Caleb McDaniel</strong>. I'm an associate professor of history at Rice University and a scholar of the nineteenth-century United States. I am also the faculty master at <a href="http://www.duncancollege.net">Duncan College</a>, the newest of Rice's eleven residential colleges.</p>

<a name="site-map"></a>

<p>On this site you can find my <strong><a href="./cv">CV</a></strong> and <strong><a href="./cv.html#publications">publications</a></strong>, occasional posts on my current <strong><a href="./research.html">research</a></strong> and <strong><a href="./teaching.html">teaching</a></strong>, and some geeky computer <strong><a href="./hacks.html">hacks</a></strong>.</p>

